<p><tags><tag kind="heading2">## </tag></tags>Tracking Progress</p>
<p></p>
<p>Did you notice the dashboard button in the toolbar? It holds detailed text statistics. You can also customize the amount of statistics on display: Just tear off the panel and click on the gear icon.</p>
<p></p>
<p>With writing goals, you can track your progress in relation to a word or character limit you determine. This sheet’s goal is “about 550 characters” - open the attachment bar to display it. Now type some words. See?</p>
<p></p>
<p>Tip: Statistics and Goals are also available for entire groups, via their context menu.</p>
